Process called "setup_kde_integration" that takes context as LinuxGUIContext returns None:
    Note: Set up comprehensive KDE Plasma integration
    Try:
        Note: Check if running under KDE
        If context.desktop_environment is not equal to KDE_PLASMA:
            Return
        
        Note: Set up KDE window decorations
        Call setup_kde_window_decorations with context as context
        
        Note: Integrate with KDE system settings
        Call integrate_kconfig with context as context and application as none
        
        Note: Set up Plasma integration if available
        Let plasma_check be execute_system_command with command as "pgrep -x plasmashell"
        If plasma_check is not equal to "":
            Call setup_plasma_integration with context as context
        
        Note: Set up KDE color schemes
        Call setup_kde_color_schemes with context as context
        
